msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງ part/partition ແລະ mount ບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ຮ່ວມກັນໄດ້"

#: ../pykickstart/commands/partition.py:488
msgid ""
"The --fstype=tmpfs option can't be used together with --grow or --maxsize"
